        <h1>Privacy Policy for PF航空词典</h1>
        <p><strong>Effective Date: September 1, 2025</strong></p>
        <p>We take your privacy seriously. This Privacy Policy explains that PF航空词典 ("the App") does not collect, use, store, or share any of your personal information or data in any form.</p>

        <h2>1. Information We Do Not Collect</h2>
        <p>We solemnly swear that the App does not contain any code or third-party services designed to collect user information. Specifically, we do not collect:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>Personal Information</strong>: We do not require or collect any personally identifiable information, such as your name, email address, phone number, or geographic location.</li>
            <li><strong>Usage Data</strong>: All functions of the App run locally on your device. We do not collect your search history, favorited words, usage frequency, app interaction data, IP address, device identifiers, or any other data related to your usage.</li>
            <li><strong>Device Information</strong>: We do not access or collect your device model, operating system version, or any other hardware or software information.</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>2. How Information Is Used</h2>
        <p>Since we do not collect any information, we do not use, process, or share your information in any way. All your data belongs entirely to you and is stored only on your local device.</p>

        <h2>3. Third-Party Services</h2>
        <p>The App does not integrate any third-party services that would collect your personal information, such as advertising networks, analytics tools, or social media plugins.</p>

        <h2>4. Contact Us</h2>
        <p>If you have any questions or suggestions about this Privacy Policy, do not hesitate to contact us:</p>
        <p>Email: yiqunzhou2@gmail.com</p>
